title: LeBron James:  Warriors 'are even more dangerous' than last year | Jan 15, 2017 | 2016-17 NBA Season
description: LeBron James doesn't consider the Warriors to be rivals and talks about the Halloween decorations poking fun at Golden State being "water under the bridge.
